high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the metal spoon out of the sink basin.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the wooden shelving unit.
Put the spoon in the grey bowl that is on the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
Pick up the grey bowl with the spoon in it off of the shelf.
Walk back over to the kitchen sink.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and locate the sink.
Pick up the spoon from inside the sink.
Hold the spoon and turn around, then face the shelf on the right.
Place the spoon in the bowl on the right side of the shelf.
Pick up the bowl from the shelf.
Carry the bowl and turn to the right and go to the sink.
Place the bowl and spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and spoon to the sink.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the spoon from the sink
Go to the shelves
Place the spoon in a bowl on the shelf
Pick up the bowl
Go to the sink
Place the bowl in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon in the sink
